                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18250915-269-off1443 t18250915-269-cd1444"></join>, and a handkerchief, value 4 s., the goods of 
                     <persName id="t18250915-269-victim1356" type="victimName">
                        James William 
                        French
                     <interp inst="t18250915-269-victim1356" type="surname" value="French"></interp>
